column2:
 Delivered projects within a budget of up to 1.5 mln USD, ensuring timely completion.

Completed English courses at the American English Center and obtained a DAO PM certificate from IAMPM.

Gained 3 years of experience in project management in an engineering company.

Design Engineer with a focus on analyzing customer design specifications and translating requirements to project teams. Committed to advancing professionally through IT Project Management certifications.

My experience includes:
- Preparation of technical and commercial proposals;
- Managing projects from contract signing to project acceptance;
- Scheduling and controlling work progress;
- Preparing questionnaires and selecting equipment;
- Supervising up to 30 design engineers;
- Coordinating project documentation with allied participants;
- Project defense;
- Creating explanatory notes;
- Organizing and attending meetings;
- Supervising on-site teams of up to 5 people;
- Conducting site visits.

PM course knowledge includes SDLC, Agile methodology, PERT estimation, risk management, PM responsibilities, communications techniques, Jira, Confluence, and Slack usage, lean canvas creation, WBS, user stories and acceptance criteria, story points, roadmap and mind map building, determining milestones, and understanding differences between waterfall and agile methodologies.
